snippet.textDisplay:
And when he grabs the mic, taking his leaps close to it, the world starts dancing with the beats in a way that says he is unbeatable!

Habib Wahid , the magician! 

When he is in the mode,  he makes you embark on a heavenly ride with his music.The beats, the soulful sound, the blend, the fusion , just speechless!  
On your first listen, you might not feel it at its best; give it a few shots and get stuck forever.
Those Persian verses were sung tremendously. However, the thirst remains unquenchable somewhere. Like in his concert, he could have showcased some instrumental magic, or another stanza of the song could have been added!
